These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-1::.
Transport: helicopter, airplane
Beverage: sprite, soy-milk
Food: peas, apricot
Pet: chinchilla, horse
Job: writer, fisherman
1. Food:apricot is on the right of Transport:helicopter##1
2. Pet:horse is on the far left##1
3. Beverage:sprite is in an even position##4
4. Job:fisherman is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Transport   | helicopter     | airplane     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk     | sprite |
| Food   | peas | apricot  |
| Pet           | horse    | chinchilla |
| Job         | fisherman   | writer       |

