.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-2::.
City: paris, prague
Color: apricot, lavender
Flower: sunflower, poppy
Transport: skateboard, subway
Sport: surfing, volleyball
1. City:paris is on the right of Transport:skateboard##1
2. Flower:sunflower == Color:apricot##1
3. Flower:sunflower is in an even position##4
4. Color:lavender is on the left or right of Sport:surfing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| City      | prague    | paris |
| Color           | lavender  | apricot     |
| Flower   | poppy       | sunflower      |
| Transport           | skateboard        | subway      |
| Sport         | volleyball | surfing     |

