Music-Genre: trance, salsa
1. House:wooden is on the left or right of City:rome##3
2. Music-Genre:trance is on the far left##1
3. Hobby:sudoku is in an odd position##4
4. Movie-Genre:romance == Music-Genre:salsa##1
5. City:rome is on the right of City:prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby         | sudoku     | puzzles    |
| Movie-Genre           | documentary     | romance |
| House   | wooden    | palace   |
| City         | prague | rome   |
| Music-Genre     | trance | salsa |

